OL,3,CThe people scared for their future as
OL,4,Cbenefit cuts announced
OL,6,FA woman from Bristol says she may lose
OL,7,Fout on vital financial support due to
OL,8,Fthe government's cuts announced in
OL,9,Ftoday's Spring Statement.
OL,11,FRuth Pickersgill has a form of
OL,12,Farthritis which affects her mobility.
OL,13,FShe receives Personal Independence
OL,14,FPayment, otherwise known as PIP, which
OL,15,Fshe says has allowed her work and
OL,16,Fvolunteer.
OL,18,FBut now, she fears she will be forced
OL,19,Fto stop if her benefits are cut.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
