OL,3,CThe people scared for their future as
OL,4,Cbenefit cuts announced
OL,6,F"PIP has been what has enabled me to
OL,7,Fwork and pay my taxes and to find now
OL,8,Fat age 70 that it's going to be taken
OL,9,Faway, I don't know what I'm supposed
OL,10,Fto do.
OL,12,F"I still volunteer almost full time
OL,13,Fand I can do those roles because I
OL,14,Fhave the support I need at home, but
OL,15,Fif you take it away, I'm stuck."
OL,17,FRuth is not alone though. Many people
OL,18,Facross the region who are disabled or
OL,19,Flive with long-term health conditions
OL,20,Fsay they have been left concerned
OL,21,Fafter today's Spring Statement.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
