OL,3,CThe people scared for their future as
OL,4,Cbenefit cuts announced
OL,6,FChancellor Rachel Reeves announced
OL,7,Fthat she would be cutting the
OL,8,FUniversal Credit health element and
OL,9,Ffreezing it until 2030.
OL,11,FThe changes came as the Office for
OL,12,FBudget Responsibility (OBR) found the
OL,13,Fpackage of benefit cuts announced last
OL,14,Fweek would not raise as much money as
OL,15,Fthe government hoped.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
