OL,3,CThe people scared for their future as
OL,4,Cbenefit cuts announced
OL,6,FThe OBR found Reeves' package would
OL,7,Fonly save #3.4 billion, rather than
OL,8,Fthe #5 billion the government hoped,
OL,9,Fbut after the further cuts, the
OL,10,Fforecaster said savings will now be
OL,11,F#4.8 billion.
OL,13,FReeves also announced the universal
OL,14,Fcredit standard allowance will now
OL,15,Fincrease from #92 per week in 2025-26,
OL,16,Fto #106 per week by 2029-30.
OL,18,F"Overall, these plans mean that
OL,19,Fwelfare spending as a share of GDP
OL,20,Fwill fall between 2026-27 and the end
OL,21,Fof the forecast period," she told MPs.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
