OL,3,CThe people scared for their future as
OL,4,Cbenefit cuts announced
OL,6,FThe other changes announced last week
OL,7,Finclude tightening the eligibility
OL,8,Fcriteria for PIP and scrapping the
OL,9,Fcontroversial work capability
OL,10,Fassessment.
OL,12,FThe government has also published its
OL,13,Fown impact assessment on how many
OL,14,Fpeople will be affected by the
OL,15,Fbenefits cuts, after resisting
OL,16,Fpublishing them until Wednesday.
OL,18,FThe assessment says 800,000 people
OL,19,Fwill be impacted by the changes to PIP
OL,20,Feligibility, losing an average of
OL,21,F#4,500 a year.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
