OL,3,CThe people scared for their future as
OL,4,Cbenefit cuts announced
OL,6,FThat includes 370,000 current PIP
OL,7,Frecipients affected and 430,000 future
OL,8,Frecipients.
OL,10,FIn Plymouth, one family have been left
OL,11,Ffearful and worried about how they
OL,12,Fwill continue to afford necessities if
OL,13,Ftheir benefits are cut.
OL,15,FDoug Kerr underwent a kidney
OL,16,Ftransplant four years ago. The
OL,17,Foperation saved his life, but last
OL,18,Fyear his body began to reject the new
OL,19,Forgan, bringing a host of new and
OL,20,Funwanted symptoms.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
