OL,3,CThe people scared for their future as
OL,4,Cbenefit cuts announced
OL,6,FHis condition means he is unable to
OL,7,Fwork and so receives PIP and Universal
OL,8,FCredit.
OL,10,F"With the PIP payment I get at the
OL,11,Fminute, it's only the lower rate. We
OL,12,Fget just over #100 a week. And that's
OL,13,Fgobbled up by going to hospital
OL,14,Fappointments, bus fares, maybe have to
OL,15,Fget an odd taxi.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
