OL,3,CThe people scared for their future as
OL,4,Cbenefit cuts announced
OL,6,F"Some of it's used for top-up on food
OL,7,Fshopping because it gets astronomical
OL,8,Fnow. And with the monthly benefit we
OL,9,Fget with Universal Credit, we find
OL,10,Fourselves at the end of the month
OL,11,Frunning low."
OL,13,FThe government is going to cut the
OL,14,Fwelfare bill by focusing on those it
OL,15,Fsays have 'higher needs'.
OL,17,F"It's going to be more difficult.
OL,18,FThere are a lot of kidney patients who
OL,19,Fare getting anxious about this change.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
