OL,3,CThe people scared for their future as
OL,4,Cbenefit cuts announced
OL,6,F"I haven't sat down and worked out how
OL,7,Fmuch we will be worse off, I just know
OL,8,Fwe will be worse off. It is going to
OL,9,Fbe a difficult time for everyone."
OL,11,FDoug's daughter, Heather, suffers with
OL,12,Ffunctional neurology disorder. Her
OL,13,Fincome could also be at risk, as the
OL,14,Fgovernment considers excluding those
OL,15,Funder 22 from incapacity benefit.
OL,17,F"Only being 19 she's going to lose out
OL,18,Fon the extra element, so yeah I think
OL,19,Fthe government is making a strange
OL,20,Fdecision on this one," Doug added.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
